params.name: vocab_size
params.description: Vocabulary size of the Pix2Struct text model. Defines the number of different tokens that can berepresented by the inputs_ids passed when calling Pix2StructTextModel.

params.name: hidden_size
params.description: Dimensionality of the encoder layers and the pooler layer.

params.name: d_kv
params.description: Dimensionality of the key, query, value projections in each attention head.

params.name: d_ff
params.description: Dimensionality of the intermediate (i.e., feed-forward) layer in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: num_layers
params.description: Number of hidden layers in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: num_heads
params.description: Number of attention heads for each attention layer in the Transformer encoder.

params.name: relative_attention_num_buckets
params.description: The number of buckets to use for each attention layer.

params.name: relative_attention_max_distance
params.description: The maximum distance of the longer sequences for the bucket separation.

params.name: dropout_rate
params.description: The dropout probability for all fully connected layers in the embeddings, encoder, and pooler.

params.name: layer_norm_epsilon
params.description: The epsilon used by the layer normalization layers.

params.name: initializer_factor
params.description: A factor for initializing all weight matrices (should be kept to 1, used internally for initializationtesting).

params.name: dense_act_fn
params.description: The non-linear activation function (function or string).

params.name: decoder_start_token_id
params.description: The id of the decoder_start_token_id token.

params.name: use_cache
params.description: Whether or not the model should return the last key/values attentions (not used by all models).

params.name: pad_token_id
params.description: The id of the padding token.

params.name: eos_token_id
params.description: The id of the end-of-sequence token.
